GLOBAL SETTLEMENT WITH U.S. DOJ, LOWER IDS EARNINGS REFLECTING A $569 MILLION NET GAIN ON THE SALE OF OUR ROCKETDYNE BUSINESS IN 2005 AND $770 MILLION OF CHARGES ON

THE AEW&C DEVELOPMENT PROGRAM IN 2006 PARTIALLY OFFSET BY IMPROVED MARGINS ON OTHER PROGRAMS AND A $320 MILLION CHARGE RELATED TO THE EXIT OF THE CONNEXION BY BOEING BUSINESS RECORDED IN OTHER SEGMENT.

