INCLUDED IN N&SS) ARE INCLUDED IN SUPPORT SYSTEMS. BUSINESS SEGMENT DATA FOR ALL PERIODS PRESENTED HAVE BEEN ADJUSTED TO REFLECT THE REALIGNMENT. SEE NOTE 22.

