FINANCIAL ACCOUNTING STANDARDS NO. 158,

EMPLOYERS ACCOUNTING FOR DEFINED BENEFIT PENSION AND OTHER POSTRETIREMENT PLANS  AN AMENDMENT OF FASB STATEMENTS NO. 87, 88, 106 AND 132(R)

(SFAS 158), WE RECOGNIZE THE FUNDED

STATUS OF OUR DEFINED BENEFIT PENSION AND OTHER POSTRETIREMENT PLANS, WITH A CORRESPONDING AFTER-TAX ADJUSTMENT TO ACCUMULATED OTHER COMPREHENSIVE LOSS. THE 2007 ANNUAL REMEASUREMENT OF OUR PENSION AND OTHER POSTRETIREMENT PLANS RESULTED IN A NET

$3,441 MILLION INCREASE IN SHAREHOLDERS EQUITY.

