OR, IN SOME INSTANCES, PRIOR TO THE END OF THE FINANCING TERM, SUCH AS CERTAIN EVENTS OF DEFAULT AND REPOSSESSION. AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2007, OUR MAXIMUM EXPOSURE TO LOSS ASSOCIATED WITH THE LOSS SHARING ARRANGEMENT WAS $224. AS OF

DECEMBER 31, 2007 AND 2006, THE ACCRUED LIABILITY UNDER THE LOSS SHARING ARRANGEMENT WAS $59 AND $78.

